dc_title_s: Glen Rock, Bergen County, New Jersey 1974
dc_description_s: Map of the Borough of Glen Rock, originally surveyed by Howard L. Boswell, borough engineer in January 1960 and revised to June 1974. In addition to the stamp from the League of Women Voters, there are also attributions printed for Piritz Harrison Corporation, Real Estate in Ridgewood, N.J. and the Borough Plan Commission of Glen Rock. Map includes full street index.
